ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2
Class ImportHandler

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.TaclanV2.ImportHandler
Direct Known Subclasses:
ESRIImportHandler, TaclanV2ImportHandler
public abstract class ImportHandler
extends Object

An abstract class specifying necessary operations for an ImportHandler in the taclan language. An ImportHandler is a class converting a importable location into ParsedDeclarations.
